title: First Academy
text: First Academy 0 comments First Academy of Leesburg 38, Jupiter Christian 8 FIrst Academy of Leesburg defeated Jupiter Christian on Friday. Quarterback Caleb Lynum was on fire for the Eagles, throwing for 243 yards and six touchdowns. He also ran for 72 yards. The top receivers for First Academy were led by Kanyon Walker who had three touchdown receptions totaling 127 yards. Taylor Lunsford and Treavon Cummings, also had touchdown receptions. Dude Edwards surpassed 150 yards rushing for the Eagles. The defense was led by Tyus Dixon, who had a great night leading in sacks and tackles for loss. Edwards and Anthony Dario kept the Jupiter offense from scoring most of the night. The FIrst Academy Eagles are now 4-4 and will face Oviedo Masters Academy on Friday.
